About Rainbow Six Siege X:
Rainbow Six Siege X is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege X is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

author: Ubisoft
description:
Anno 117: Pax Romana is out now and it’s time to take up the mantle of a Roman governor in charge of building a new, thriving city. Doing so is easier said than done and before you build Rome’s next metropolis, you’ll need to get the basics down. Thankfully, we got you covered with everything you need to know:

Step 1: Start Timber Production
Step 2: Building Roads and Warehouses
Step 3: Understanding Your Residents
Step 4: Growing Your Income
Step 5: Pay Attention to Where You Place Your Buildings
 
Follow these 5 simple steps and you’ll be well on your way to building a city to rival Rome itself. 

About Anno 117: Pax Romana:
In the latest instalment of the award-winning Anno strategy franchise, it’s your destiny to shape the Roman Empire in the year 117 AD. As governor, will you encourage economic growth or expand your rule through dominance? Lead with rebellion or unite a diverse culture? 
The cost of peace is yours to decide.

Learn more about Ubisoft: www.ubisoftgroup.com
